dct_title_s: 1913 road map of Santa Cruz County, California
dct_description_sm: compiled by E.D. Rodgers ; W.H. Oliver, draughtsman.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map given in "Miles."
Shows topography of peaks, drainage, towns, roads, railroads, schools.
Imprint taken from verso of map.
